🇺🇸若遵憲法學校是不可禁止學生穿著便服讀書
🇺🇸因憲法無法讓台灣人自小習慣做國民黨奴隸
🇺🇸故國民黨棄中華民國憲法效法英日獨裁體制
🇺🇸就讓蔡國獨裁合體吧別再欺騙世人及台灣人
🇺🇸免憂台灣被人類看穿就是一黨獨大獨裁國家

snippet.textDisplay: Man.. this was one of the best all star games I've ever seen. It had all the 'fun' plays early on, with the dunks and alley oops, but then they played some tight defense with lots of steals/blocks too. It got real in the 4th quarter, no one let the other team run away with it from lack of interest. It's also crazy how much smoother these guys look compared to watching play from the 80s and 90s. The worst guy on the court just looks better handling the ball or scoring then half the allstars from back then.
